  <summary date="2021-02-01T21:28:57Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Military Domestic Violence Prevention Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense to take various actions and implement programs related to the prevention of and response to domestic violence and child abuse and neglect among military families, including by ensuring information sharing among the Armed Forces about incidents reported to the Family Advocacy Programs of the Armed Forces.</summary>
